        <td id="descriptionArea">
            <h3><a name="Objective"></a>Objective</h3>

<p>Complete the beta version of the product.</p>

<h3><a name="Context"></a>Context</h3>

<p>Each team member has specific roles and tasks. This epic focuses on finalizing the beta version to evaluate the product's structure before the production release.</p>

<h3><a name="Scope"></a>Scope</h3>

<ul>
	<li><b>Included</b>: Development and completion of the beta version.</li>
	<li><b>Not Included</b>: Production release and post-launch activities.</li>
</ul>


<h3><a name="Successcriteria"></a>Success criteria</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Beta version is completed on time.</li>
	<li>The structure of the product is clearly defined and understood.</li>
</ul>


<h3><a name="Risksanddependencies"></a>Risks and dependencies</h3>

<ul>
	<li>Potential delays in task completion from team members.</li>
	<li>Dependencies on team collaboration and communication.</li>
</ul>


<h3><a name="Otherinformation"></a>Other information</h3>

<p>N/A</p>
